    "### Component 5 — Automation Artefact\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "**System:** AI-Driven Transaction Fraud Detection System (UK Retail Banking)  \n",
    "**Frameworks:** EU AI Act (2024) · UK AI White Paper (2023) · UK GDPR · FCA Consumer Duty · Equality Act 2010  \n",
