    "| 4 | **Stakeholder Risk Register** | Full risk register sorted by severity |\n",
    "| 5 | **Regulatory Obligations Table** | Mapped legal obligations with applicability ratings |\n",
    "\n",
    "> **EU AI Act Classification: 🔴 HIGH RISK** — Annex III §5(b): AI in essential private services (banking)\n",
